{"tid":126598,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"河北一KTV爆炸 網民：如火山噴發","createTime":"2017-02-19T13:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T13:21:57.000Z","uid":38539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d64f54aacf639b91ae3a5cb90e3b7c5c3f2bbd00","tid":126598,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2017/02/480ce15c58f8821_size566_w237_h191.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F480ce15c58f8821_size566_w237_h191.gif&h=ba64b38a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【大紀元2017年02月17日訊】2月17日13時許，河北承德市一家飯店的KTV突然發生爆炸，目前有2人受傷送醫救治。網民稱，爆炸威力如火山噴發，現場有一輛公交車玻璃被震碎，嚴重受損。附近居民透露，實際爆炸自中午11時許開始，至1時許共有3次爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n據鳳凰網報導，經排查，爆炸原因初步認定為盛華大酒店南側地下燃氣管道泄漏所致。已有2名受傷KTV員工被送往醫院治療。<br />\n<br />\n有網民發布消息指，爆炸地點位於承德雙橋區武烈路和新華路交匯的盛華大酒店和錢庫KTV附近。爆炸威力如火山噴發，現場濃煙滾滾，爆炸的衝擊波還導致一輛公交車嚴重受損。<br />\n<br />\n一位居住在附近的民眾對大紀元記者表示，他在家裡一共聽到三聲爆炸，第一聲爆炸大概在中午11時許，聲音特別大，「噹」的一聲，然後隔了20多分鍾，又一聲巨響，第三聲爆炸大約在1時許，聲音沒有前兩次那麼響。<br />\n<br />\n截至發稿時間，未見有對事件的進一步報導。<br />\n<br />\n醬油﹕<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/2/17/n8820438.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F17%2F2%2F17%2Fn8820438.htm&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmq0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=9a319184\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/2/17/n8820438.htm</a>"},{"pid":"48e4fa34433fadbbc77e51b3dc28510db32e56b2","tid":126598,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uoW_6ALIIv4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuoW_6ALIIv4&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmq0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=87291758\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uoW_6ALIIv4</a><br />\nTVBS NEWS"},{"pid":"2d202a11ae722a84bd7f611995831cb2d7e1804b","tid":126598,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:17:34.000Z","msg":"藝術"},{"pid":"e2b04e7d0411c43f5e12302b132fa91b57506689","tid":126598,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藝術</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/26741.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F26741.jpg&h=f7941500&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac39716e104a33061823cc940c38b542b0743e4b","tid":126598,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>藝術</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/26741.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F26741.jpg&h=f7941500&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/56579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F56579.jpg&h=6d910bc2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}